  <div class="ct">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Where to go next</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:14px;">The support pages that actually help.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 28px;max-width:70ch;">Each of these routes a real intent &mdash; honestly. They tell you what Intuit owns and what an independent Certified ProAdvisor does, and they never imply this firm is Intuit.</p>
